      </list>
      <para id="id1171802171047">Everyone is unique and their differences should be respected and not made fun of.</para>
      <list id="id1171807895409" list-type="bulleted">
        <item>Human rights</item>
      </list>
      <para id="id1171802920588">Everyone has rights – even the handicapped.</para>
